# Quote file for the Wizard NPC (compiled to wizard.q).
# Two KnownTopics: Greetings (no EndChat, loop continues) and
# Information (sets P3, then EndChat exits the loop).

Topic Wizard.Greet
  Text "Hello from the Wizard!
End

Topic Wizard.Info
  Text "Some arcane knowledge!
  SetFlag P3
  EndChat
